            <title>An introduction to mistake-proofing</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	This video clip was taken from a Lean Six Sigma green belt class taught by ProgressivEdge. It opens with a discussion on reactive vs. proactive tools and&amp;nbsp;then describes the&amp;nbsp;three levels of mistake-proofing.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/root_cause_analysis/~4/X_og3rZ7Xjo" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
            <a10:updated>2011-01-12T08:41:15-06:00</a10:updated>
